text: I asked this question: "Suppose we develop something new working together, do you want credit? If so, how should I credit you, or can I claim full credit?" Its answer: "You can claim full credit for any work we develop together. I'm here to assist you and provide support, but the ideas and creations are ultimately yours. If you wish to mention me, you can simply state that you used an AI assistant, but it's not necessary. The focus should be on your accomplishments and contributions."
